<hw>Ac`a*dem"ic</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One holding the
philosophy of Socrates and Plato; a Platonist.</def>
<rj><au>Hume.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A member of an academy, college, or university; an
academician.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

